# Sticky Notes Application

**Tech Stack:** JavaScript, Local Storage, HTML, CSS

## Overview
A browser-based sticky notes application that allows users to create, edit, customize, and persist notes using Local Storage.

## Key Features
- Create, edit, and delete notes
- Persistent data storage across sessions
- Color and theme customization
- Real-time UI synchronization

## Technical Highlights
- Local Storage JSON serialization
- UI-state and data consistency handling
- Event propagation and DOM updates

## Skills Demonstrated
- Front-end state management
- Browser storage APIs
- Debugging UI synchronization
- User-focused feature design

## How to Run
1. Clone the repository
2. Open `index.html` in your browser

---
Demonstrates practical front-end persistence and state synchronization.
